      <item>
        <title>Generalized Pareto distribution (GPD)</title>
        <description>&lt;script type=&quot;math/tex; mode=display&quot;&gt;gpd(x) = 1 - (1+\frac{\xi X}{\beta})^{\frac{-1}{\xi}}&lt;/script&gt;

&lt;p&gt;note its similarity to the &lt;a href=&quot;generalized-extreme-value-distribution.html&quot;&gt;GEV&lt;/a&gt;(generalized extreme value distribution).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;with &lt;script type=&quot;math/tex&quot;&gt;\xi &gt; 0&lt;/script&gt; this distribution also shows significant &lt;strong&gt;fat tails&lt;/strong&gt;. &lt;script type=&quot;math/tex&quot;&gt;\beta&lt;/script&gt; is a scaling factor.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This distribution was derived using the peaks-over-threshold method: the conditional probability of a loss above a defined threshold.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
        <pubDate>Tue, 29 Mar 2016 00:44:01 +0200</pubDate>
        <link>http://codiepp.github.io/Hedge-o-Mat/Hedge-o-Mat/statistics/generalized-pareto-distribution.html</link>
